           SPELL=init.d
         VERSION=1.08
         ENTERED=20020719
         UPDATED=20030723
      MAINTAINER=eschabell@sourcemage.org
           SHORT='Install functions and selected system scripts then sets runlevels and  priorities.'
cat << EOF

Installs and sets runlevel priority on basic system init scripts, such 
as localtime.sh, mount.sh and  mountnfs.sh.
It includes functions script modified from LFS-3.1. Originally rewritten 
by Gerard Beekmans - gerard@linuxfromscratch.org, with code based on Matthias 
Benkmanns simpleinit-msb http://winterdrache.de/linux/newboot/index.html. 

Modified for Source Mage GNU/Linux.

EOF
